<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Thanksgiving_(United_States)&action=edit&section=25.php.html" title="Edit section: Music">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Music">Music</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>"Thankgiving Day", a song by <a href="Ray_Davies" title="Ray Davies">Ray Davies</a> on his 2006 album <i><a href="Other_People's_Lives" title="Other People's Lives">Other People's Lives</a></i></li>
</ul>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Thanksgiving_(United_States)&action=edit&section=26.php.html" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Notes">Notes</span></h2>
